  <summary date="2020-07-29T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Congressman John R. Lewis Election Day Act of 2020

This bill designates November 3, 2020, as a legal public (i.e., national) holiday known as John Lewis Election Day. It also urges U.S. private employers to give their employees the day off on November 3, 2020, so they may cast votes in elections held on that day.</summary>
